---
title: Cherry Balsamic Chicken with Almond Couscous & Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Over here, we believe chicken is a canvas, and we like to paint it with allllll the flavors. Tonight’s palette: A saucy coating that includes glossy cherry jam and balsamic pan sauce—because why choose one of these ingredients when you could have both? Add to that a side of almond-studded couscous and roasted Brussels sprouts, and you have yourself a dinner to Remem-brandt (see what we did there?).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/649aea3dc8e13be2fa91de06-43d3eddc.jpeg
